Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.03,0:00:35.89,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}毁灭终结的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.45,0:00:45.51,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}无情的宣告
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.04,0:00:58.40,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}你独自听到了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.81,0:01:11.23,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}我做了一个遥远的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.66,0:01:13.16,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}该选择什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.16,0:01:14.68,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}该放弃什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.68,0:01:16.38,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}该决定什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.38,0:01:17.91,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}我算什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.91,0:01:19.51,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}该选择什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.51,0:01:21.13,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}早已经决定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.13,0:01:22.66,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}有没有做错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.66,0:01:24.17,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(50,50)}对着神质问
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.17,0:01:26.96,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}我并非独自一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.38,0:01:36.71,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}你一直在身边 对我伸出这双手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.05,0:01:39.89,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}没什么好害怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.21,0:01:51.66,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}即便化为怪物也要完成愿望
