Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.96,0:02:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.56,0:02:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.18,0:02:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.63,0:02:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.69,0:02:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按开演时间来看 来得是不是太早了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.30,0:02:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是为了买演唱会商品
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.33,0:02:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束之后再买不行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.02,0:02:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正常来说热门商品到时候就会卖光的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.37,0:02:28.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.23,0:02:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说 你也是个蛮狂热的歌迷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.24,0:02:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 昨天怎么不跟莎拉见见面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.22,0:02:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是对T恤衫和钢笔那类东西感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.27,0:02:42.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想要那个手机的高机能外壳而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.86,0:02:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内藏电池 还附带高音质线性PCM录音机哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.07,0:02:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦 那还真棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.89,0:02:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不想买吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.34,0:02:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是买的话我俩就凑成一对了 你不介意吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.99,0:02:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.64,0:02:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么请你千万别买
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.88,0:03:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的还真干脆啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.37,0:03:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点受打击..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.90,0:03:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好长的队伍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.76,0:03:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能老老实实排了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.29,0:03:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还傻站着干嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.86,0:03:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我又不买啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.66,0:03:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不买也要跟着来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.55,0:03:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人排队连聊天对象都没有会很无聊的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.67,0:03:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来这家伙 原本不是讨厌我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.80,0:03:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又邀请我来演唱会..又叫我一起排队..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.17,0:03:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么关系又变好了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.65,0:03:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望还没卖光啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.82,0:03:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.42,0:03:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那个..
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.85,0:03:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是觉得这队伍真的好长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.49,0:03:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是 毕竟是世界性的人气乐队啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.91,0:03:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来这种大神才不会在这类小场子办演出啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.62,0:03:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙 很厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.79,0:03:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手机壳GET！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.33,0:03:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊看啊 快看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.91,0:03:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何啊 这背面的LOGO
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.73,0:03:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZHIEND这几个字的造型美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.13,0:04:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我觉得很好看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.76,0:04:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.49,0:04:07.88,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇~太溜了~好帅~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.21,0:04:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到底还是很狂热呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.05,0:04:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.05,0:04:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的眼前被漆成一片碧绿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.28,0:04:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从未被发现
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.49,0:04:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我玩捉迷藏的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.05,0:04:46.12,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,lying before me scene painted in green
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.28,0:04:50.94,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was never found 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.49,0:04:58.36,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,when I played hide & seek
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.36,0:05:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的脸上留下一道小小的伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.93,0:05:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你低头跪地 苦苦支撑 好似身受重伤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.36,0:05:04.48,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,there remains a little scar on your face still facing down
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.93,0:05:12.52,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to the ground you hold yourself and crouch like you've been wounded
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怀念我们无忧无虑胡思乱想的岁月
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.62,0:05:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怀念你静静靠在我身边的岁月
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.00,0:05:19.62,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I adored the days when we just thought the thing with no means oh
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.62,0:05:26.67,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I adored when you were always just there for by my side
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.33,0:05:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不可思议的感觉是怎么回事..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.06,0:05:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 我们要在可爱的日本来一首全球首次公开的歌曲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.94,0:05:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRIGGER
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.31,0:05:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.49,0:05:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往毁灭 前往黑暗深渊 我的未来和预料的一样孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.87,0:05:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正往那里进发
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.31,0:05:45.08,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,come now 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.49,0:05:52.60,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,heading to the oblivion to the darkness sink me future is lonely as it seems to be
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.87,0:05:54.69,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and I am reaching for there
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.40,0:06:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个曲子我有印象..明明应该从没听过啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.09,0:06:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的思路从未如此清晰 我觉得只要我愿意 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.34,0:06:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就无所不能
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.97,0:06:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感到被人唾弃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.93,0:06:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道你能掌控什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.07,0:06:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你了解我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.47,0:06:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不停地旋转
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.26,0:06:29.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不停地来回 你会作为天使降临于此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.71,0:06:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深深坠落
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.23,0:06:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一面黑暗正在等待着我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:37.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永不终结
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.22,0:06:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超越边界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.62,0:06:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.09,0:06:12.34,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My mind is clear now I feel like I can do anything
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.34,0:06:14.48,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,when I want to do it,yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.97,0:06:18.54,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I feel I'm notorious 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.93,0:06:21.73,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what you can handle?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.07,0:06:24.25,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.47,0:06:26.26,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Spinning round and round
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.26,0:06:29.71,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,going back and forth will be here as an angel
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.71,0:06:31.86,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that's fallen deep
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.23,0:06:35.31,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,see there's the dark side waiting for me
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:37.22,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,never end forever
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.22,0:06:38.62,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,out on the rim 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.62,0:06:41.47,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,no need to breathe ever I'm
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.61,0:06:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有宇哥哥 你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.74,0:06:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 ZHIEND的新歌实在是太震撼了..
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.30,0:07:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZHIEND果然很厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.50,0:07:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们的歌一定会让我毕生难忘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.82,0:07:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论今后发生什么事..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.15,0:07:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那边呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.16,0:07:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,HaloHalo果然还是一如既往的HaloHalo是也
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.22,0:07:13.12,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D区域的晚餐时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.68,0:07:14.32,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.90,0:07:16.68,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D区域的晚餐时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.30,0:07:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 肚子饿扁了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.19,0:07:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是这个老爷爷么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.37,0:07:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他为什么一直待在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.28,0:07:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古典音乐很好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.89,0:07:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清澈无比 就像计算公式一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.77,0:07:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是你的妹妹吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.12,0:07:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.93,0:07:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗..真可怜..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.93,0:07:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,研究者之中也有人对我们抱有这类的感情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.32,0:07:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你一直待在这里呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.81,0:07:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于我提出了太过离奇..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.40,0:07:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者说对研究者不利的假设而一直备受嘲笑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.60,0:07:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我在这里借曲消愁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.79,0:08:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道天动说吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.25,0:08:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 名字有听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.78,0:08:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在想来是很离奇的理论 不过当时却是普遍的观点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.44,0:08:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是事实并非如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.93,0:08:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认为第一个提出异议的人结果如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.50,0:08:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道..
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.47,0:08:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他被视为异端 遭受众人挤兑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后落得一事无成的下场
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.33,0:08:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像现在的我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.47,0:08:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了 今天是咖喱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.62,0:08:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定又放了促进能力的化学物质 尝起来一股药味吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.09,0:08:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此 步未认为咖喱还是蕴含着让人幸福的美味呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.02,0:08:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼哥哥要是在的话就好了 三人一起吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.18,0:08:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥的能力太过突出了 不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.96,0:08:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的能力是什么来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.75,0:08:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时空穿越..timeleap
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.17,0:09:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那太厉害了啦..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.95,0:09:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为那个能力太厉害了 他才被关起来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.85,0:09:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隼哥哥好可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 所以别再提起这个话题了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.62,0:09:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.16,0:09:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一如既往的药味
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.97,0:09:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们认为我的能力仅仅是能够附身他人五秒 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.37,0:09:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真正的能力被发现的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.59,0:09:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该会像哥哥一样被完全剥夺自由
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.11,0:09:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过如果一直继续接受检查的话 应该很快会被发觉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.90,0:09:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见 就这样安静听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.13,0:09:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊耳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.67,0:09:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.49,0:09:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于找到了心灵感应能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.81,0:09:51.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.96,0:09:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.91,0:09:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且既能接收也能发送讯息
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.16,0:09:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.15,0:09:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那个人被关起来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.20,0:09:59.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.99,0:10:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先附到右后方的大背头身上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.02,0:10:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是我带来的粉碎能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.27,0:10:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过能力并不强
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.24,0:10:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.22,0:10:14.82,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.94,0:10:16.97,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇？这是怎么回事啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.29,0:10:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来是心灵感应能力者的所在地 收下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.08,0:10:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千万注意行动时机
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.40,0:10:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对我们来说是唯一的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.27,0:10:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失败的话你会被处分掉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.76,0:10:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我们也将步上你的后尘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.34,0:10:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.67,0:10:38.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊耳那家伙 真的去和那个胆小鬼见面了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.97,0:10:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎哟 七野 你嫉妒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.25,0:10:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.93,0:10:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一直在等待这一天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.47,0:10:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟只有在这个关头 他的那位弟弟才会认真起来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.32,0:10:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是个妹控而已啊 整天跟妹妹玩在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.97,0:10:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为如此啊 我们只能相信他了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.68,0:11:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这场豪赌 到底能有多少胜算呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.84,0:11:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事不是100%怎么行 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.54,0:11:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失误是决不允许的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.84,0:11:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 你的能力什么时候能发挥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.54,0:11:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可是出色完成了寻找心灵感应能力者的任务哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.61,0:11:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就会看到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.94,0:11:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对会挑个大场面施展出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.12,0:11:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那是死亡flag
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.18,0:11:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不会死啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.88,0:11:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不准聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.01,0:11:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.38,0:11:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界..真的会改变吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.99,0:11:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间到了 回去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.49,0:11:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放风结束了么..真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.02,0:11:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.78,0:11:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 是不是拿到了什么东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.93,0:11:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.53,0:11:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.97,0:11:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位先生的待遇为什么跟我们不一样呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.11,0:11:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他虽然没有哥哥那么厉害 但也是个相当强的能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.59,0:12:06.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来 救出哥哥的准备就做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.80,0:12:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 就看什么时候动手了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.76,0:12:16.73,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的程序已经结束
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.31,0:12:19.07,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了接到传唤通知的实验对象
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.49,0:12:21.39,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其余人等请迅速回到自己的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.57,0:12:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.64,0:12:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 说起来步未被叫到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.57,0:12:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？这么重要的事怎么不早点说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.10,0:12:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.22,0:12:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 这太奇怪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.16,0:12:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有能力的妹妹 怎么会遭到传唤呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.97,0:12:38.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有宇哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.31,0:12:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步未
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.82,0:12:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地震吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.97,0:12:49.40,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D区域已经被封锁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.19,0:12:52.29,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在收到下一指示前请待在原处
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.22,0:12:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生了什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.40,0:12:54.01,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.81,0:12:56.18,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D区域已经被封锁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.78,0:12:59.26,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在收到下一指示前请待在原处
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.42,0:12:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有非常不好的预感..
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.93,0:13:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快开门啊 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.31,0:13:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.56,0:13:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.44,0:13:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.75,0:13:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步未她怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.72,0:13:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你妹妹的能力被强行激发出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.62,0:13:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能力是“崩坏”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.63,0:13:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D区域之所以被封锁 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.75,0:13:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为她的能力让设施处于半毁状态
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.50,0:13:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步未呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.58,0:13:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她没事 但是由于她的能力太过危险
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.81,0:13:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在已经被拘禁起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.08,0:13:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和哥哥一样么..
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.50,0:13:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这意味着她会在解剖后被处分掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.33,0:13:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还傻站着干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.81,0:13:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要使用你真正的能力就能救她了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.32,0:13:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.49,0:13:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名为“掠夺”的最强能力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.20,0:14:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会知道这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.31,0:14:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这些 现在时间不多了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.85,0:14:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 他说的对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.65,0:14:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.04,0:14:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下我也要被处分掉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.15,0:14:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方是心灵感应能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.41,0:14:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去除杂念..去除杂念..去除杂念..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.40,0:14:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.92,0:14:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑子里出现声音？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.48,0:14:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是心灵感应能力吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.07,0:14:36.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找我有什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.42,0:14:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要看到脸的话..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.69,0:14:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸..怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.42,0:14:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 没你什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.47,0:14:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.11,0:14:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 站住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.39,0:14:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等一下如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.80,0:15:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个..没必要消除这个人的记忆吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.12,0:15:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望如此吧..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.67,0:15:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.19,0:15:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我出去 让我出去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.49,0:15:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,B区域封锁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.28,0:15:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.78,0:15:09.46,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.86,0:15:11.55,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,D区域发生紧急事件
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.13,0:15:14.83,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有职员请按规定就位
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.01,0:15:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 到底发生了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.29,0:15:20.45,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我..救救我..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.39,0:15:21.97,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.36,0:15:24.13,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 让我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.41,0:15:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都可以 请告诉我？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.54,0:15:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个声音..连方向都能确定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.16,0:15:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 你听得见我的声音吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.90,0:15:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是有宇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.96,0:15:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有宇？你吸收了那种能力么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.09,0:15:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被发现的话就糟糕了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.70,0:15:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的状况已经管不了那么多了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.65,0:15:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步未要被解剖了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.55,0:15:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步未？为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.50,0:15:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她拥有了足以破坏设施的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.73,0:15:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连步未都..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.31,0:15:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会把哥哥救出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.07,0:15:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以请你穿越时空 改变这个世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.37,0:15:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算怎么过来这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.28,0:15:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 只要眼睛能接触到光的话..
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.70,0:15:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.03,0:15:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.67,0:16:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七野？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.52,0:16:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 为什么要为了你这种妹控..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.96,0:16:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生了什么..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.56,0:16:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没时间了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.33,0:16:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快夺走我的穿透能力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.06,0:16:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.06,0:16:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说没时间了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.23,0:16:19.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.91,0:16:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走这边 快点去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.00,0:16:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 不过哥哥他会帮我们改变世界的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.18,0:16:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个能力怎么回事..好累人..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.45,0:16:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.56,0:16:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得到了七野的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.91,0:16:45.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在就来 哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.70,0:16:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.05,0:17:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了啊 有宇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.10,0:17:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我必须马上去才行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.79,0:17:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 之后就拜托你了 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.54,0:17:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 为了未来..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.92,0:17:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是为了大家..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.48,0:17:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改变世界
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.34,0:17:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,处分！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.78,0:17:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别吓我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.59,0:17:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.61,0:17:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是医院
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.98,0:17:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在演唱会中昏倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.84,0:17:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还记得吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.28,0:17:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗..步未她已经..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.54,0:17:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做恶梦了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.06,0:17:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.54,0:17:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚才看到的真的是梦吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.06,0:18:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 之前步未也说过 她觉得我们还有另一位家人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.15,0:18:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最好还是再躺一会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.23,0:18:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说不定有个哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.68,0:18:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不..应该有的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.74,0:18:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.75,0:18:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你想起来了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.90,0:18:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.06,0:18:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特殊能力发现能力者..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.45,0:18:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说更明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.89,0:18:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.92,0:18:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干了之后倒是蛮帅的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.89,0:18:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的梦里你也出现了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.42,0:18:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个样貌你应该是第一次见到才对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.26,0:18:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊耳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.51,0:18:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也认识我哥哥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.69,0:18:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦..是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.95,0:18:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请把一切告诉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.12,0:18:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先冷静 我正是为此而来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.50,0:18:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安静跟我来的话 你的所有疑问就会引刃而解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.73,0:18:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后你要去救她 救你的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.62,0:18:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才..说什么..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.71,0:19:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去拯救你的妹妹 乙坂有宇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.63,0:19:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死掉的人要怎么救？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.67,0:19:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的你 应该知道你哥哥隼翼的能力了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.11,0:19:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.81,0:19:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 你说的隼翼先生 是指那个隼翼先生吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.73,0:19:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 没错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.33,0:19:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是那个人的弟弟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.01,0:19:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.66,0:19:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么都行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.08,0:19:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我也能去见他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.75,0:19:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为好久没见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.31,0:19:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们什么关系？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.71,0:19:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥变成废人之后 是他为我指明了前进方向
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.83,0:19:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到了唯一能够相信的人 直到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.59,0:19:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是我的哥哥吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.96,0:19:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.14,0:19:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.56,0:20:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这里开始要步行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.42,0:20:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.95,0:20:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟我们最不缺的就是钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.63,0:20:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.13,0:20:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简单而言 就是特殊能力的研究设施
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.66,0:20:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们对我们来说不是敌人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.41,0:20:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 别啰嗦跟着来就是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.48,0:20:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 我可以拍吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.45,0:20:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以就怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.56,0:20:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好严密啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.47,0:20:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这里是最后的堡垒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.44,0:20:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥..就在前面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.18,0:21:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有宇吗 好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.29,0:21:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我带他们来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.28,0:21:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.37,0:21:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是..哥哥吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.42,0:21:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他没想起来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.31,0:21:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来 前泊消除的记忆他并没有想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.28,0:21:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消除的记忆？那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.00,0:21:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听这声音是奈绪酱吗？好久不见了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.59,0:21:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.75,0:21:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还在按照你所指明的道路前进呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.87,0:21:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏你帮了我不少忙 你干的很好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.13,0:21:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢夸奖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.76,0:21:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.73,0:21:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 有宇你呢？我可是你的大哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.53,0:22:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是感动的再会啊 不过来好好抱抱吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.85,0:22:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在..有些混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.85,0:22:04.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满脑子都是问号
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.15,0:22:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 真叫人寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.09,0:22:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可话说回来 这也是自作自受么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.76,0:22:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么全都说给你听吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.49,0:22:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧？噗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.40,0:22:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.81,0:22:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么开始讲述我那漫长的时空穿越的故事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.13,0:22:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好感兴趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.45,0:22:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他要..开始讲述什么呢？
